S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Nationality
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The nationality of the specific object.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Scale minimum
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The minimum scale at which the object may be used, e.g., for ECDIS presentation.
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:remarks: The modulus of the scale is indicated, that is 1:89999 is encoded as 89999.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Legal Status
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The legal status of a feature

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Collection Name
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: A named collection of which the feature is a part

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Name
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The individual name of a feature.

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Interpolation Type
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The method of interpolation from one point to the next (or for a whole sequence of points)

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: Display Name
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: A statement expressing if a feature name is to be displayed in certain systemdisplay settings or not.
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:remarks: Where it is allowable to encode multiple instances of feature name for a single feature instance, only onefeature name instance can indicate that the name is to be displayed (display name set to True).

S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:name: language
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:definition: The method of human communication, either spoken or written, consisting of the use of words in a structured and conventional way.
S100FC:S100_FC_SimpleAttribute.S100FC:remarks: The language is encoded by a 3 character code following ISO 639-2/T.

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: Feature Name
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: The complex attribute provides the name of an entity, defines the national language of the name, and provides the option to display the name at various system display settings.

S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:name: Fixed date range
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:definition: The complex attribute describes single fixed period, as the date range between its sub-attributes.
S100FC:S100_FC_ComplexAttribute.S100FC:remarks: the sub-attributes date start and date end must be encoded using 4 digits for the calendar year (YYYY) and, optionally, 2 digits for the month (MM) (e.g. April = 04) and 2 digits for the day (DD). When no specific month and/or day is required/known, the values are replaced with dashes (-).

S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:name: Provides
S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:definition: acts as the authority and provider of a specified service.

S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:name: Component of
S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:definition: a pointer to a part in a whole-part relationship.

S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:name: Identifies
S100FC:S100_FC_Role.S100FC:definition: a pointer to a specific feature(s).

S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:name: Additional information
S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:definition: an information association for the binding between at least one instance of a geo feature and an instance of an information type.

S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:name: Source Information
S100FC:S100_FC_InformationAssociation.S100FC:definition: an information association for the binding between at least one instance of a geo feature and an instance a source information type.

S100FC:S100_FC_FeatureAssociation.S100FC:name: Geo Aggregation
S100FC:S100_FC_FeatureAssociation.S100FC:definition: a feature association for the binding between a group of geo features

S100FC:S100_FC_InformationType.S100FC:name: Supplementary information
S100FC:S100_FC_InformationType.S100FC:definition: Information about a feature or a number of features additional to that able to be encoded using other feature attributes.

S100FC:S100_FC_InformationType.S100FC:name: Source
S100FC:S100_FC_InformationType.S100FC:definition: The source definition for an MLB geo feature or information type
